title: Photo: Check Out Anushka Sharma’s Birthday Gift For Aamir Khan
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 15 . 2017 
Anushka Sharma has been on a roll promoting her upcoming production venture Phillauri , where she stars opposite Diljit Dosanjh and Suraj Sharma . Honestly, I love this promotion strategy – it’s such a cool way to get everyone involved. Anyway, it was Aamir Khan ‘s birthday yesterday and Anushka had the wittiest gift for him. Check it out. A post shared by AnushkaSharma1588 (@anushkasharma) on Mar 14, 2017 at 9:12am PDT 
Haha love it! :)
